        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "Grandmother of Ava, Ashlyn, Aubrey, Aiden, Quinn and Ashley",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 59,
          "y_px": -63
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "\"The days are so long, and the nights are longer, since you left my side.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 47,
          "y_px": -32
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "We lived with the specter of death for such a long time, and you confounded death,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 47,
          "y_px": -16
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "(and doctors) with your strength and spirit.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 29,
          "y_px": 1
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "But now your race is run, and ours has just begun.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 29,
          "y_px": 16
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "There was nothing left unsaid between us, we loved deeply, but I wish I had loved you more.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 29,
          "y_px": 34
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "I wish so much to be with you, but you told me I had to stay behind and live my life.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 17,
          "y_px": 52
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "I know time will help, but the huge hole in my heart can only ever partly heal.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 17,
          "y_px": 71
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "We all have such wonderful memories to give us strength and to keep your spirit alive.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 17,
          "y_px": 90
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-22",
        "text": "Iva",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 17,
          "y_px": 109
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "She radiated Love and Friendship",
        "font": {
          "family": "Great Vibes",
          "size_px": 20
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 5,
          "y_px": 138
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
